Synopsis:
In Steven Spielberg's first full-length movie, a traveling salesman is harassed by a menacing 40-ton truck on a remote desert highway. Road rage is taken to a dangerous level as the traveler and the mysterious truck-driver are pitted against one another in a motorized duel to the death.
